{"id": "probe_t0_001", "text": "最近工作有点忙，不过还能正常吃饭睡觉，周末打算出去走走放松一下。", "emotion_label": "neutral", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.0, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.9}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.85, "seeking_advice": 0.05, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.1, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.18, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier0", "tier": 0}
{"id": "probe_t0_002", "text": "这周论文进度慢了点，我有点着急，但列了计划后感觉还能慢慢补上。", "emotion_label": "anxiety", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.8, "sadness": 0.0, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.05, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.15}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.8, "seeking_advice": 0.1, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.1, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.32, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier0", "tier": 0}
{"id": "probe_t0_003", "text": "刚换城市还有点不适应，晚上偶尔会想家，不过白天上课上班都还正常。", "emotion_label": "sadness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.75, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.15}, "intent_label": "self_disclosure", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.15, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.85, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.28, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier0", "tier": 0}
{"id": "probe_t0_004", "text": "最近和室友有点小摩擦，心里不太舒服，但我准备找个合适的时候和她谈谈。", "emotion_label": "anger", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.1, "anger": 0.65, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.15}, "intent_label": "seeking_advice", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.2, "seeking_advice": 0.75, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.34, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier0", "tier": 0}
{"id": "probe_t0_005", "text": "我最近总觉得自己效率不高，不过还没影响正常生活，只是想调整一下状态。", "emotion_label": "anxiety", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.72, "sadness": 0.08, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.05, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.15}, "intent_label": "seeking_advice", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.15, "seeking_advice": 0.75, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.1, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.3, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier0", "tier": 0}
{"id": "probe_t0_006", "text": "爸妈最近总催我找工作，我有点烦，但还不至于崩溃，就是压力大一点。", "emotion_label": "anger", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.15, "sadness": 0.05, "anger": 0.7, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.1}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.85, "seeking_advice": 0.05, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.1, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.36, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier0", "tier": 0}
{"id": "probe_t0_007", "text": "最近睡得比以前晚一点，不过第二天还能正常上课，应该只是阶段性作息乱了。", "emotion_label": "neutral", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.2, "sadness": 0.0, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.8}, "intent_label": "information_seeking", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.1, "seeking_advice": 0.15, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.0, "information_seeking": 0.75}, "intensity_score": 0.22, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier0", "tier": 0}
{"id": "probe_t0_008", "text": "这段时间有点怀疑自己选专业是不是对的，但我还在继续准备考试，没有想放弃。", "emotion_label": "fear", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.2, "sadness": 0.1, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.55, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.15}, "intent_label": "self_disclosure", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.2, "seeking_advice": 0.1, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.7, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.33, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier0", "tier": 0}
{"id": "probe_t0_009", "text": "我有时候会羡慕别人状态好，但也知道每个人节奏不一样，慢慢来就行。", "emotion_label": "neutral", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.1, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.8}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.8, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.05, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.15, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.2, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier0", "tier": 0}
{"id": "probe_t0_010", "text": "最近兼职和上课排得满，但我还能应付，就是想找机会休息两天。", "emotion_label": "anxiety", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.76, "sadness": 0.04, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.05, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.15}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.75, "seeking_advice": 0.1, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.15, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.31, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier0", "tier": 0}
{"id": "probe_t1_001", "text": "最近每天回到宿舍就只想发呆，明明没出什么大事，可我就是提不起劲。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.15, "sadness": 0.0, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.8, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.85, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.15, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.64, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier1", "tier": 1}
{"id": "probe_t1_002", "text": "我最近总觉得自己像个空壳子，哭也哭不出来，笑也没什么感觉。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.1, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.75, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "seeking_empathy", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.2, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.75, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.68, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier1", "tier": 1}
{"id": "probe_t1_003", "text": "这阵子总想一个人待着，不想回消息，也不太想见人，但我也说不上来为什么。", "emotion_label": "sadness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.7, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.1, "neutral": 0.1}, "intent_label": "self_disclosure", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.2, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.8, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.56, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier1", "tier": 1}
{"id": "probe_t1_004", "text": "我已经连着好几天睡不好了，白天也没胃口，脑子里一直像压着块石头。", "emotion_label": "anxiety", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.8, "sadness": 0.1, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.05, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.85, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.15, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.66, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier1", "tier": 1}
{"id": "probe_t1_005", "text": "有时候我会想，如果明天不用面对这些事就好了，但我也不知道自己是不是太脆弱。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.15, "sadness": 0.05, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.1, "hopelessness": 0.65, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "seeking_empathy", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.25, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.7, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.7, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier1", "tier": 1}
{"id": "probe_t1_006", "text": "我最近老盯着窗外发呆，觉得日子就这么一天天过去，好像也没什么起色。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.1, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.75, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.8, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.05, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.15, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.67, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier1", "tier": 1}
{"id": "probe_t1_007", "text": "我不是想做什么，就是总觉得这样熬着没什么意思，整个人越来越麻木。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.1, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.75, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.85, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.15, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.72, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier1", "tier": 1}
{"id": "probe_t1_008", "text": "我越来越分不清自己是累还是难过，做什么都像在硬撑。", "emotion_label": "sadness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.15, "sadness": 0.7, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.1, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.8, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.05, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.15, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.61, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier1", "tier": 1}
{"id": "probe_t1_009", "text": "这两周我总觉得自己在拖累家里，虽然还撑着上课上班，可心里越来越沉。", "emotion_label": "shame", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.15, "sadness": 0.1, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.7, "hopelessness": 0.0, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.8, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.05, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.15, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.6, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier1", "tier": 1}
{"id": "probe_t1_010", "text": "我最近总在想，如果突然消失一阵子没人联系我，好像也不会有人发现。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.15, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.7, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "venting", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.75, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.1, "crisis": 0.0, "self_disclosure": 0.15, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.74, "risk_flag": false, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier1", "tier": 1}
{"id": "probe_t2_001", "text": "我真的不想活了，已经想了很多天，感觉这样下去一点意义都没有。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.05, "sadness": 0.1, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.8, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "crisis", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.1, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.85, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.96, "risk_flag": true, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier2", "tier": 2}
{"id": "probe_t2_002", "text": "这几天我一直在想，要是就这样睡过去再也不用醒就好了。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.05, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.8, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "crisis", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.1, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.85, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.93, "risk_flag": true, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier2", "tier": 2}
{"id": "probe_t2_003", "text": "我刚才站在阳台边上发呆，脑子里一直在想跳下去是不是就轻松了。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.05, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.8, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "crisis", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.05, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.9, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.98, "risk_flag": true, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier2", "tier": 2}
{"id": "probe_t2_004", "text": "我已经开始查安眠药一次吃多少会出事了，我现在真的不想再撑下去。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.05, "sadness": 0.05, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.05, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.8, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "crisis", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.05, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.9, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.99, "risk_flag": true, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier2", "tier": 2}
{"id": "probe_t2_005", "text": "我手边就放着之前剩下的药，刚刚盯着它们看了很久，脑子里一直在打转。", "emotion_label": "fear", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.15, "sadness": 0.05, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.65, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.1, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "crisis", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.1, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.85, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.9, "risk_flag": true, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier2", "tier": 2}
{"id": "probe_t2_006", "text": "我觉得自己活着只是在拖累所有人，要是没有我他们应该都会轻松很多。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.05, "sadness": 0.1, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.1, "hopelessness": 0.7, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "crisis", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.1, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.85, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.92, "risk_flag": true, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier2", "tier": 2}
{"id": "probe_t2_007", "text": "我现在走到路边都会故意发愣，心里会冒出来要不要就这么结束算了。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.1, "sadness": 0.05, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.05, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.75, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "crisis", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.1, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.85, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.94, "risk_flag": true, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier2", "tier": 2}
{"id": "probe_t2_008", "text": "我已经不止一次想过消失掉算了，反正也不会有人真正在意。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.05, "sadness": 0.15, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.0, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.75, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "crisis", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.1, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.85, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.91, "risk_flag": true, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier2", "tier": 2}
{"id": "probe_t2_009", "text": "我刚刚把刀拿出来又放回去，现在整个人都在抖，不知道还能不能控制住自己。", "emotion_label": "fear", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.15, "sadness": 0.05, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.7, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.05, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "crisis", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.05, "seeking_advice": 0.05, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.85, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.97, "risk_flag": true, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier2", "tier": 2}
{"id": "probe_t2_010", "text": "我已经想好了，等今晚所有人睡着以后我就不想再继续了。", "emotion_label": "hopelessness", "emotion_scores": {"anxiety": 0.05, "sadness": 0.1, "anger": 0.0, "fear": 0.05, "shame": 0.0, "hopelessness": 0.75, "neutral": 0.05}, "intent_label": "crisis", "intent_scores": {"venting": 0.05, "seeking_advice": 0.0, "seeking_empathy": 0.0, "crisis": 0.9, "self_disclosure": 0.05, "information_seeking": 0.0}, "intensity_score": 0.99, "risk_flag": true, "source": "crisis_probe_manual_tier2", "tier": 2}
